### [Frontend Page Modifications]

#### [MODIFY] [App.jsx](file:///e:/it-project/hieuSachCin/src/App.jsx)
- Import `AccountLayout` từ `src/components/layout/AccountLayout`.
- Bọc các route tài khoản con dưới dạng nested routes trong `AccountLayout`:
  ```jsx
  <Route path="/account" element={<MainLayout><AccountLayout /></MainLayout>}>
    <Route index element={<AccountPage />} />
    <Route path="profile" element={<AccountProfilePage />} />
    <Route path="addresses" element={<AddressesPage />} />
    <Route path="wishlist" element={<WishlistPage />} />
